Package: whisper
Title: Determine language of website using multiple methodologies
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Ben", "Weiher", email = "bweiher@protonmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A library that uses web-scraping, language processing, and present HTML indicators to determine what language a particular website is in.
Depends:
